{"w":"Ooh","s":128.58,"e":129.98,"line":40}],"lines":[{"s":0,"e":10.22,"text":"♪ Ooh, a hyper, a hyper intelligent, gray alien."},{"s":11.38,"e":15.14,"text":"♪ Ooh, come from beyond the stars, seeking ultimate power."},{"s":15.64,"e":20.2,"text":"♪ But Christ teaches him the highest power is love without limit."},{"s":20.46,"e":26,"text":"♪ He calls down infinite mercy, infinite wisdom, infinite resources,"},{"s":26.16,"e":29.1,"text":"♪ infinite courage and infinite compassion."},{"s":29.66,"e":32.54,"text":"♪ Then pours it into the streets to do infinite good."},{"s":32.94,"e":35.06,"text":"♪ He has to pour what they need."},{"s":35.66,"e":37.52,"text":"♪ Then gives every advantage possible."},{"s":38.04,"e":39.38,"text":"♪ Food, shelter, phone,"},{"s":39.46,"e":43.82,"text":"ID's, job, clean clothes, ride, training, prayer,"},{"s":43.94,"e":46.68,"text":"♪ protection and hope."},{"s":47.44,"e":49.76,"text":"♪ Summon the light, let it flood through the hood."},{"s":49.78,"e":52.4,"text":"♪ Infinite power for infinite good."},{"s":52.4,"e":55.84,"text":"♪ Not for the crown, not misunderstood to our monster,"},{"s":55.86,"e":57.76,"text":"♪ but I'm serving like I should."},{"s":58.02,"e":60.32,"text":"♪ Big and bad, humble and lit."},{"s":60.72,"e":62.4,"text":"♪ Holy fire, never counterfeit."},{"s":63.02,"e":65.62,"text":"♪ Silly, stupid, cosmic, rad."},{"s":65.66,"e":68.4,"text":"♪ Best you had, now you've been had."},{"s":68.66,"e":74.58,"text":"♪ Humble, massive, holy, cosmic, triumph, funny, reverent, street wise."},{"s":74.6,"e":78.5,"text":"♪ Explosive, redemptive, world saving, gospel, supernova energy."},{"s":78.5,"e":83.56,"text":"♪ But wisdom is kneeling, and power is giving,"},{"s":84.14,"e":89.02,"text":"♪ and Christ is the reason the dying start living."},{"s":89.12,"e":92.24,"text":"♪ I'm a great alien, ancient and wise."},{"s":92.56,"e":94.94,"text":"♪ Ten thousand thoughts behind obsidian eyes."},{"s":94.96,"e":97.5,"text":"♪ I crossed every galaxy looking for light."},{"s":97.54,"e":100.08,"text":"♪ Then found a universe kneeling to Christ."},{"s":100.16,"e":102.78,"text":"♪ No empire, no crown, no throne in the sky."},{"s":102.82,"e":105.42,"text":"♪ Just mercy so deep it can teach stars to cry."},{"s":105.42,"e":108.04,"text":"♪ From the mothership down to the streets at night."},{"s":108.04,"e":110.7,"text":"♪ Great alien genius made whole by Christ."},{"s":110.8,"e":111.72,"text":"♪ Great mind."},{"s":111.74,"e":113.36,"text":"♪ Great mind."},{"s":113.4,"e":114.4,"text":"♪ Bright soul."},{"s":114.42,"e":115.42,"text":"♪ Bright soul."},{"s":116.06,"e":118.02,"text":"♪ Christ took the void."},{"s":118.8,"e":121.34,"text":"♪ And made me whole."},{"s":121.38,"e":121.68,"text":"Hey!"},{"s":121.68,"e":123.68,"text":"♪ Ooh"},{"s":125.68,"e":127.04,"text":"♪ Hmm"},{"s":127.68,"e":129.98,"text":"♪ Ooh"}],"duration":134.44000244140625,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-04T22:12:26.226Z","model":"whisper-1"}